17
00:01:37,161 --> 00:01:38,961
And just a reminder of what that means.

18
00:01:39,621 --> 00:01:51,885
It means that it is importantly associated with one or more historic persons or events, or with the broad architectural, cultural, political, economic, or social history of the city or the Commonwealth,

19
00:01:52,665 --> 00:02:06,508
or it is historically or architecturally important in terms of period, style, method of building construction, or association with an important architect or builder, either by itself or in a group of buildings.

20
00:02:07,288 --> 00:02:13,570
So last month we had a significance hearing and 56 Wareham was found to be significant.

21
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:18,995
So tonight we will determine if the property is to be preferably preserved.

22
00:02:19,496 --> 00:02:31,929
And what that means is that the commission has determined after an open public hearing that the demolition of the building under review would be detrimental to the architectural or historical heritage of the city of Medford.

23
00:02:32,670 --> 00:02:45,135
